metadata.description: CRAZY BEANZ NFTZ is a collection of 3,333 animated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. All CRAZY BEANZ come holding a SCRATCHIEZ that serves as ticket to win more prizes at the SCRATCHIEZ BOOTH, winners are stored in our FREEZER-OF-FAME. All CRAZY BEANZ get access to illusive 7-A-LEMON, a Sanbox world where anything goes, what could possibly go wrong!? Visit www.crazybeanz.io to learn more.
